text: Otto Roesner (December 22, 1881 - August 1951) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1951 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lansing, Michigan
